msgid "Downgrade from 5.0 to 4.10"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/downgrade.rst:9
msgid ""
"During the version 5.0 upgrade process, a migration is run to enable new "
"features of the `advanced permissions system "
"<https://docs.mattermost.com/deployment/advanced-permissions.html>`__. "
"This changes the database in ways that result in it no longer being "
"compatible with Mattermost server 4.10. If you need to downgrade from 5.0"
" or later to 4.10, it is necessary to follow the steps below."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/downgrade.rst:11
